      <H2><font color= "FF9933">Lawson LID</font></H2>
      <br />
      The HyperLearn method of LearnMode is the recommended way to learn Lawson LID forms. Refer to <a href="https://perceptivesoftware.secure.force.com/articles/Support_Articles/Article-000015524?popup=true">HyperLearn Overview </a> in Knowledgebase for tips when using HyperLearn. In some instances, there may be a need to <a href="https://perceptivesoftware.secure.force.com/articles/Support_Articles/Article-000015557?popup=true">remove unwanted spaces when linking</a>, the need to <a href="https://perceptivesoftware.secure.force.com/articles/Support_Articles/Article-00001553?popup=true">convert uppercase to lowercase letters</a> or to <a href="https://perceptivesoftware.secure.force.com/articles/Support_Articles/Article-000015568?popup=true">replace apostrophes with commas in a name field</a> to successfully complete the linking process using HyperLearn.  
      <br />
      <br />
